00:07:50.374 --> 00:07:53.232
Now, I feel strongly about 
poetry for what it offers in 

00:07:53.233 --> 00:07:55.233
these terms, but I 

00:07:56.282 --> 00:07:59.157
also, more and more, recognize 
its value as a remedy to the 

00:07:59.158 --> 00:08:01.158
various things that 

00:08:03.026 --> 00:08:05.463
have bombarded our lines of 
sight and our thoughts, and that

00:08:05.464 --> 00:08:07.464
tamper with our 

00:08:10.345 --> 00:08:12.165
ability or even our desire to 
