00:08:32.181 --> 00:08:34.181
in our browser sidebars, in the 
pages 

00:08:35.650 --> 00:08:38.088
of present media, embedded in 
movies and TV shows, on 

00:08:38.089 --> 00:08:40.089
airplanes, and taxis, and 

00:08:41.141 --> 00:08:43.141
trains, and even toilet stalls.

00:08:44.802 --> 00:08:46.841
I guess more and more I see the 
technology we live, listening 

00:08:46.842 --> 00:08:49.078
for and hearing into, as the 
primary and most 

00:08:52.744 --> 00:08:54.744
effective vehicle of that sales 
pitch.

