00:11:24.796 --> 00:11:26.427
Poetry is one vehicle for this 
humanizing version of language, 

00:11:26.428 --> 00:11:29.280
because the features of the poem
insist upon a 

00:11:34.519 --> 00:11:39.669
different value system. Rather 
than numbing or drowning out the

00:11:39.670 --> 00:11:41.506
difficult to describe, but 
urgently sensed feelings that 

00:11:41.507 --> 00:11:46.816
are part of being human, poetry 
invites us to tease them out, to

00:11:46.817 --> 00:11:48.817
draw them into language that is 

00:11:51.501 --> 00:11:53.752
rooted in intricate thought and 
strange impulse. Rather than 

00:11:53.753 --> 00:11:56.398
putting up a buffer between 
ourselves and those outside our 

00:12:01.722 --> 00:12:03.565
immediate sphere, poems devise 
means to contemplate those 

00:12:03.566 --> 00:12:05.566
others and to take in their 
perspective.

00:12:06.805 --> 00:12:08.805
Rather than solving, 
side-stepping, 

00:12:11.268 --> 00:12:12.696
or denying problems, poems bear 
witness to dark facets of 

00:12:12.697 --> 00:12:18.222
experience. They give us 
vocabulary for the terror, the 

00:12:18.223 --> 00:12:20.223
shame, the regret, as well as 
the 

00:12:21.684 --> 00:12:23.684
