00:12:33.507 --> 00:12:36.152
And they ask us to submit to 
another experience of reality.

00:12:40.026 --> 00:12:42.679
They disorient us from our home 
base and they teach us to admit 

00:12:42.680 --> 00:12:44.680
and submit to 

00:12:45.757 --> 00:12:48.011
the feeling of  vulnerability, 
to act upon empathy and 

00:12:48.012 --> 00:12:50.012
curiosity, and to 

00:12:51.099 --> 00:12:53.099
follow along, allowing sense to 
accrue 

00:12:55.403 --> 00:12:57.403
at its own pace and upon its own
terms.

00:12:57.457 --> 00:12:59.690
If you do that enough times with
