00:14:04.910 --> 00:14:06.910
of sharing, and following, or 
buying and 

00:14:07.960 --> 00:14:09.960
wearing, but rather that of 
bearing deep 

00:14:11.205 --> 00:14:13.205
and un-abashed witness to the 
urgencies 

00:14:14.672 --> 00:14:16.672
and upheavals of lived 
experience that 

00:14:17.925 --> 00:14:19.925
comes closest to bringing us 
into 

00:14:21.383 --> 00:14:23.383
